 ***voting eligibility
	We should receive 3 inputs from the user 
	Name 
	Gender
	Age
	Criteria 1: less than 18 years irrespective of gender NOT ELIGIBLE 
  Criteria 2: if someone is more than 60 irrespective of gender ELIGIBLE 
  Criteria 3: if gender is male they have rights to vote only if above 30***



-->CODE

Name=str(input("Enter Name:"))
Gender=str(input("Enter Gender:"))
Age=int(input("Enter Age:"))
if Age<18:
   print("Not eligible")
elif Age>60:
   print("Eligible")
else:
    if Gender=="M" and Age>30:
        print("Eligible")
    else:
        print("Not Eligible")


